Output help.gif
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontSize 32
Set Width 2400
Set Height 700
Set Framerate 30
Set Padding 20
Hide
Type "cargo build --example help 2>/dev/null"
Enter
Sleep 5s
Type "cargo run --example help 2>/dev/null"
Enter
Sleep 1s
Show
Sleep 2s
Type "k"
Sleep 1s
Type "j"
Sleep 1s
Type "?"
Sleep 3s
Type "?"
Sleep 2s
Type "q"
